Halo SDK Patch for @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk 0.2.87
=========================================================

This file signals the deployment system to upload the locally patched SDK.

The actual patching is done by scripts/patch-sdk.mjs, which:

1. Forwards cwd to ProcessTransport (fixes remote working directory)
   - Adds: cwd:$.cwd, stderr:$.stderr, sandbox:$.sandbox

2. Forwards all SDK options instead of hardcoding them
   - extraArgs, maxTurns, maxBudgetUsd, fallbackModel, etc.

3. Passes systemPrompt via initConfig to Query
   - Enables custom system prompt for remote sessions

4. Adds session control methods to Tz class
   - interrupt(), setModel(), setMaxThinkingTokens(), setPermissionMode()
   - get pid (for process health tracking)

5. Removes CLAUDE_CODE_ENTRYPOINT to appear as native CLI
6. Removes CLAUDE_AGENT_SDK_VERSION to appear as native CLI

Run: node scripts/patch-sdk.mjs
